<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="70" >Keuzer@Quelliousさんは No.7512「A spirit (StoneBrunt)」で書きました。
>猫村のそばに一匹だけSensetheDeadに反応する赤いWispがいました。
>名前はa spirit。
>
> You say, 'Hail, a spirit'
> a spirit flares brightly as you attempt to speak with it. By 
>listening very closely you're brely able to make out it's frantic 
>whispering. It keep refering to one of the Kejekans, one that 
>apparently slew him as he attempted to cleanse the land of them. It 
>wants nothing more than to destroy who killed him, but it cannot in 
>this [form]. 
> You say, 'what is form'
> a spirit flares brightly again as it explains there isn't enough 
>time for it to explain. It then begins to whisper again, telling you 
>that it commands you the aid it in it's revenge. You make out, 
>through the barely audible whispering, that if you do help it, you 
>will be rewarded. 
> You say, 'what is revenge'
> a spirit whispers that he will need to become whole again before he 
>can defeat the fool animal that slew him. The spirit admits to one 
>mistake before coming here to wipe the Kejekans. In an earlier 
>campaign, he lost a very powerful weapon. That weapon would enable 
>him to take on a form likened to his former self. If you return this 
>weapon to the spirit, and then help him to defeat his enemy, the 
>reward will be yours. 
>
</TEXTAREA><br>
